Empty can runs were done for background subtraction.

LA-3765 (1967) are slightly different from those in
Tables I+II of LA-3765 (1967) and Tables 1+2 of
Nucl.Phys.A107(1968)139. Values in Appendix A are
adopted in this EXFOR entry except for 005 and 015.
